a, Our Garden fresh salads come from our indoor garden.The Food Network has featured our New Mexico Green Chile Bread. Empanadas, Pizzas, Our Turkey Bread Sculptures. And Biscochitos. We also carry beer and wine", photoCount: "136.0", ratingHistogram: "{\"count1\": 11, \"count2\": 17, \"count3\": 39, \"count4\": 200, \"count5\": 649}", email: "chrismorales@goldencrown.biz", website: "http://www.goldencrown.biz", rankingPosition: "2.0", hours: "{\"weekRanges\": [[{\"open\": 600, \"openHours\": \"10:00\", \"close\": 1200, \"closeHours\": \"20:00\"}], [], [], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1200, \"closeHours\": \"20:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1200, \"closeHours\": \"20:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1200, \"closeHours\": \"20:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1200, \"closeHours\": \"20:00\"}]], \"timezone\": \"America/Denver\"}", address: "1103 Mountain Rd NW, Albuquerque, NM 87102-1865", neighborhoodLocations: [], dishes: ["Salad", "Chili", "Cakes", "Empanadas", "Empanada", "Cake", "Pastries", "Cookies"], reviewTags: "[{\"text\": \"empanadas\", \"reviews\": 270}, {\"text\": \"bread\", \"reviews\": 226}, {\"text\": \"pizza\", \"reviews\": 441}, {\"text\": \"sandwiches\", \"reviews\": 118}, {\"text\": \"blue corn\", \"reviews\": 59}, {\"text\": \"coffee milkshake\", \"reviews\": 17}, {\"text\": \"chilli\", \"reviews\": 96}, {\"text\": \"salad\", \"reviews\": 52}, {\"text\": \"free cookies\", \"reviews\": 10}, {\"text\": \"wedding cookies\", \"reviews\": 9}, {\"text\": \"sweet potato\", \"reviews\": 20}, {\"text\": \"guy fieri\", \"reviews\": 9}, {\"text\": \"old town\", \"reviews\": 61}, {\"text\": \"crust\", \"reviews\": 151}, {\"text\": \"panaderia\", \"reviews\": 35}, {\"text\": \"peasant\", \"reviews\": 16}, {\"text\": \"apricot\", \"reviews\": 22}, {\"text\": \"loaves\", \"reviews\": 9}, {\"text\": \"patio\", \"reviews\": 56}, {\"text\": \"herbs\", \